## Deny Categories

| Category | Matches When |
|----------|--------------|
| WARRANTS | subject.hasWarrant === true |
| REPLICANTS | subject.type === 'REPLICANT' |
| ENGINEERS | subject.occupation === 'ENGINEER' |
| SYNTHETICS | type in ['REPLICANT', 'CONSTRUCT'] |
| TITAN ORIGIN | subject.origin === 'TITAN' |
| IO ORIGIN | subject.origin === 'IO' |
| NON-HUMANS | type !== 'HUMAN' |

